    "Description": "The initial \"engagement\" was a decoy to lure part of the Robotech forces away from the SDF-1.   Zentraedi/Zentradi main attack force press forward.\n\nWe have Destroid Spartans, Defenders and Monsters joining the fray.  Battling various configurations of Regults and Glaugs.\n\nOur third attempt at playing around with the Robotech/Macross universe.   Also there were a few requests to get their callsign on the side of the VF-1's, check it out.\n\n___________________________\n\nIf you want to Buy us a Coffee,\nJust click the link below:\nhttps://www.buymeacoffee.com/ironcastle\nThanks for your support!",
